  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "薛家湾供电公司关于办理内蒙古嘉洋科技有限公司年产8000吨电子级硅烷项目配套110kV供电线路工程用地范围内文物保护许可的请示",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "center",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": null,
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": true
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "准格尔旗文物局[]：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "内蒙古嘉洋科技有限公司年产8000吨电子级硅烷项目配套110kV供电线路工程由我公司承担建设，目前该项目已由鄂尔多斯市能源局核准，本项目为薛家湾地区“十四五”输电网规划项目，可改善并优化准格尔旗地区的电网结构[]。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "一、项目名称",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "内蒙古嘉洋科技有限公司年产8000吨电子级硅项目配套110kV供电线路工程。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "二、建设规模及主要建设内容",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "内蒙古嘉洋科技有限公司年产8000吨电子级硅项目配套110KV供电线路工程大路、光明220kV变电站各扩建1个110kV输电线路工程，路径长度约16.4km（双回路架空线路工程约14.3km，单回路架空线路约1.7km，电缆约0.4km）；新建大路-嘉洋110kV输电线路工程路径长约4.56km（双回路架空线路约3.8km，单回路架空线路约0.43km，电缆约0.33km），新建钢管杆120基。随线路新建0PGW光缆。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "三、建设地点",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "项目位于鄂尔多斯市准格尔旗大路镇大沟村，东孔兑村，何家塔村境内。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "四、项目用地面积",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "内蒙古嘉洋科技有限公司年产8000吨电子级硅项目配套110kV供电线路工程，拟占地面积0.1148公顷。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "按照各级文物管理要求及《内蒙古自治区文物局关于做好基本建设用地考古工作的通知》（内文物发（2025）6号）文件要求，特向贵局申请核查本项目建设用地范围内是否涉及文物保护单位，恳请贵局早日核实并出具相关审查意见。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
